    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Youri Matiounine</b>\n</p><p><b>Youri Matiounine</b>,<br />\nan American <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Actuary\">actuary</a> at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_Life_Insurance_Company\">New York Life Insurance Company</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. As computer games programmer, Youri Matiounine is author of the <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> bot <i>Ymatioun</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, open source under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GNU GPL v3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> using <a href=\"/AVX2\" title=\"AVX2\">AVX2</a> intrinsics and some <a href=\"/X86-64\" title=\"X86-64\">x86-64</a> <a href=\"/Assembly\" title=\"Assembly\">assembly</a> with AVX2 instructions, and the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and later <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Fizbo\" title=\"Fizbo\">Fizbo</a>, introduced in May 2014 to <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, which became <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source</a> in October 2019 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2013_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Youri_Matiounine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013_...\">2013 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Youri_Matiounine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2013 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50150\">handling draw by insufficient material</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, November 19, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Draw_Evaluation\" title=\"Draw Evaluation\">Draw Evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/Material#InsufficientMaterial\" title=\"Material\">Insufficient Material</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51134\">problem with syzygy tablebases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51518\">SEE logic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a>, <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=7523\">new engine - Fizbo - could you please test it?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, May 07, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=7826\">Fizbo version 1.3 is released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, November 11, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Youri_Matiounine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=65466&amp;start=7\">Re: Tapered Eval between 4 phases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 16, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a>, <a href=\"/AVX\" title=\"AVX\">AVX</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66090\">Fizbo 2 has been released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2017</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Youri_Matiounine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pub/youri-matiounine/5/67/704\">Youri Matiounine | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/fizbochessengine/\">Fizbo Chess Engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://code.google.com/p/ymatioun/\">ymatioun - code of YMATIOUN Othello bot - Google Project Hosting</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Youri_Matiounine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pub/youri-matiounine/5/67/704\">Youri Matiounine | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_Othello#List_of_Top_Othello.2F_Reversi_Programs\">List of Top Othello/ Reversi Programs - Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://code.google.com/p/ymatioun/\">ymatioun - code of YMATIOUN Othello bot - Google Project Hosting</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=7523\">new engine - Fizbo - could you please test it?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, May 07, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72021\">Fizbo 2 sources just got released</a> by Damir, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 06, 2019</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/MoonstoneLight/Fizbo-Chess\">GitHub - MoonstoneLight/Fizbo-Chess: Original codes of Fizbo Chess</a>. Thanks to original author <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Youri Matiounine</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301153841\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 